Tanitani have question for
experienced adventurer-like friends!

rows.label: qst500103_msg0003
rows.name:
Friends think juice made with
Blue Ladybird be tasty-tasty?

rows.label: qst500103_msg0008
rows.name:
This juice will be ultra
popular! Eclipse even shiny
success of famous Twinklejuice!

rows.label: qst500103_msg0010
rows.name:
But friends not pros in juice
making industry. Tanitani probably
should not listen to opinion.

rows.label: qst500103_msg0011
rows.name:
Tanitani think Blue Ladybird tastiest
of all bug. Put into juice will make
perfect blend of tasty-tasty goodness.

rows.label: qst500103_msg0012
rows.name:
Soon Twelve Brothersisterpon
be most popular drinks place
in all Avaritia once again!

rows.label: qst500103_msg0013
rows.name:
Oh yes, Tanitani have other
brotherpons and sisterpons also
searching for tasty-tasty ingredients.

rows.label: qst500103_msg0014
rows.name:
Maybe friends meet them during travel.
Make sure say hello-lo if yes!
